Thank you @SUNY &amp; Syracuse for your partnership!

When I announced that New York was transitioning to zero emissions vehicles by 2035, we became global leaders on clean transportation. Proud to stand with the international community on today's landmark
@COP26 transport declaration. Learn more: https://t.co/czXsEoMhm7
#RouteZero https://t.co/6S26VWbGLy

We've brought New York to the front of the pack &amp; delivered nearly $1B for renters struggling from the pandemic. 

But we must do more.

@USTreasury is taking applications from states needing more funds &amp; I’m making sure New York is first in line to get additional relief.

This holiday season, we want New Yorkers to be able to travel &amp; for visitors to enjoy all New York has to offer without increased stress.

@SenSchumer is right: TSA workers must get their shots now so they can keep our airports running smoothly.
https://t.co/Pu4AiWJazq
